# 🧠 AI Business Analyst Agent

This project is an AI-powered Business Analyst that combines:

- 📊 SQL-based data analysis (PostgreSQL)
- 📄 Document intelligence (RAG)
- 🤖 LLM reasoning (Llama 3 via Ollama)

---

## 🚀 Features

- Natural language → SQL queries
- Semantic document search
- Combined reasoning (data + context)
- Business-style insights

---

## 🧱 Tech Stack

- Python
- PostgreSQL (Docker + pgvector)
- Ollama (Llama 3)
- Sentence Transformers
- LangGraph (planned)

---

